A simple ember.js app with ember-i18n for translations


To run the ember.js app locally

    npm install
    gulp

    python -m SimpleHTTPServer 3000

    visit http://localhost:3000 to see the running app


To run the javascript tests

    npm install
    gulp test


The bulk of the interesting code is in the bootstrap init code

https://github.com/toranb/ember-translations-example/blob/master/js/app/initializers/bootstrap.js#L10
